    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Get ready to enjoy the ride in this wonderful find! This car is in truly good condition, having been well-maintained and cared for by its previous owner. It runs smoothly and looks great, making it a dependable and stylish choice for anyone looking for a quality vehicle that's ready for the road. While it shows the expected light wear of a pre-owned car, it remains a fantastic and reliable option!",
